Package: transcripTools
Title: Collection of functions for analysing gene expression data 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Dominic", "Pearce", email = "dominic.pearce@ed.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Allows id conversion and replacement, most variable gene calling, 
    expressionSet building and both MDS and heatmap data formatting for plotting
    via ggplot2.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.1)
License: MIT + file
Encoding: UTF-8
